<div class="home-header d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
  <div class="container col-xxl-10 px-4 py-5">
    <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-1 py-5">
      <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-5">
        <%# <img src="bootstrap-themes.png" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Bootstrap Themes" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy"> %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7 pt-3">
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold lh-sm mb-3 text-white">A beautiful online travel journal for every traveller.</h1>
        <h5 class="lead pb-3 fw-bold text-dark"><span class="home-highlight">Never lose a travel memory again</span></h5>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start mb-3">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to "Create post", new_post_path, class: "btn btn-primary px-4 btn-lg me-md-2 home-btn" %>
            <%= link_to "My posts", posts_path, class: "btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4 fw-bold" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Create account", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary px-4 btn-lg me-md-2 home-btn" %>
            <%= link_to "Explore", explore_path, class: "btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4 fw-bold" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row py-3 pb-5 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h2 class="text-center fw-bold">Take your travel experiences with you everywhere 🌎</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row text-center g-5 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-sm-8 col-lg-4">
      <h4 class="fw-bold pb-3"><span class="highlight">Create a trip ✈️</span></h4>
      <p>'Europe Trip 2021'.</p>
      <p>'Honeymoon in Korea'.</p>
      <p>'Amazon River Trip 2022'</p>
      <p>A trip is the foundation of every travellers journey. It is a collection of small, daily adventures that lead us outside of our comfort zones and into the unknown.</p>
      <p>Whether by plane, train or automobile, a few days or a few years - the trip is what encompasses every experience.
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <h4 class="fw-bold pb-3"><span class="highlight">Write a post ✏️</span></h4>
      <p>Travel journaling is unique because it is is one of the few things that isn't done for anyone else - it is just for you.</p>
      <p>If you want to share your travel pics with friends and get tonnes of likes there are other sites for that - this is about cherishing your personal experiences through words.</p>
      <p>Every day of your trip, take 5 minutes to create a post - tagging your location, uploading one photo (Yes - just one) and journaling about your adventures.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <h4 class="fw-bold pb-3"><span class="highlight">Share a travel hack 🤝</span></h4>
      <p>Help other travellers in the community by sharing the highlight of your day and one valuable tip that you wish you had known ahead of time.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
